{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/spring-restapi-01.md/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"spring-tools-suits이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spring-tools-suits%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"spring tools suits이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Spring Tools Suits이란?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>STS란 이름에서도 알 수 있듯이 스프링 통합 개발 환경을 제공하는 툴이며 스프링을 개발하는데 많은 편의 기능을 제공한다.</p>\n<p>STS 다운로드 : <a href=\"https://spring.io/tools\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://spring.io/tools</a></p>\n<p>위 주소로 접속하면 아래와 같은 화면을 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/29114/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/c8a19b8596169e6f857c188bcc379ab1/29114/1.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>자신의 OS에 맞게 설치해주면 된다.<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/29114/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/efc66/2.png 885w,\n/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/c83ae/2.png 1180w,\n/static/9b466fcd559622711a2d43de6538ffc5/29114/2.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>처음 STS를 실행하면 볼 수 있는 화면이다.<br>\n이클립스나 intelliJ와 흡사한 인터페이스를 띄고있다.<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/29114/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/fcda8/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/12f09/7.png 148w,\n/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/e4a3f/7.png 295w,\n/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/fcda8/7.png 590w,\n/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/efc66/7.png 885w,\n/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/c83ae/7.png 1180w,\n/static/89a9e8942daf6fa087ff4684236fd831/29114/7.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>새 프로젝트를 생성하기 위해서 왼쪽 상단의 file - New - Spring Starter Project를 클릭 해주자.<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/29114/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/fcda8/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/12f09/8.png 148w,\n/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/e4a3f/8.png 295w,\n/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/fcda8/8.png 590w,\n/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/efc66/8.png 885w,\n/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/c83ae/8.png 1180w,\n/static/41e33b2d429d3ffd57af8fb7c11efd60/29114/8.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>다른건 건들이지말고 name만 정해주자. 나는 demo로 생성해줬다.<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/29114/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"9\"\n        title=\"9\"\n        src=\"/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/fcda8/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/12f09/9.png 148w,\n/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/e4a3f/9.png 295w,\n/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/fcda8/9.png 590w,\n/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/efc66/9.png 885w,\n/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/c83ae/9.png 1180w,\n/static/8f1ca57a3827b8130311a072b322af4f/29114/9.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>다음으로 디펜던시를 추가해줘야하는데 우리는 Web에서도 Spring Web을 사용하기 때문에 해당 항목만 체크해주고 넘어가자.</p>\n<p>이 다음 화면으로 패키지 설치화면이 나올 수도 있는데 마찬가지로 다음을 눌러주자.<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/29114/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/fcda8/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/12f09/10.png 148w,\n/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/e4a3f/10.png 295w,\n/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/fcda8/10.png 590w,\n/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/efc66/10.png 885w,\n/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/c83ae/10.png 1180w,\n/static/4d8a29da34f47a18018e8cb376d5231a/29114/10.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>프로젝트 생성 후 프로젝트를 오른쪽 클릭후 Run as - Spring Boot App을 클릭시 프로젝트를 실행할 수 있다.<br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 341px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6b2baf19206d1a496178a08c9b920612/4c0ad/11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 4.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAR0lEQVQI1x2KMQoAIQzA7mkiTkWhi20dRPyA/99y6BCSId9ai947OWfM7PX1JSKoteLuiAhjDFprqCopJfbenHMopbx/zskPK4knl4ZW0MEAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"11\"\n        title=\"11\"\n        src=\"/static/6b2baf19206d1a496178a08c9b920612/4c0ad/11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b2baf19206d1a496178a08c9b920612/12f09/11.png 148w,\n/static/6b2baf19206d1a496178a08c9b920612/e4a3f/11.png 295w,\n/static/6b2baf19206d1a496178a08c9b920612/4c0ad/11.png 341w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 341px) 100vw, 341px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><br>아래 터미널 로그를 확인해보면 8080 port로 로컬 서버가 열린 것을 확인해볼 수 있다.\nLocalhost:8080으로 접속시 확인할 수 있다.<br><br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5dc12a9fa5e4d1afe4c96d3d34f589e2/29114/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIW